node.text:
There are so many people out there saying that they want to save to invest, save for a big purchase, or save for a rainy day…

But when the right investment comes along…

When they find the perfect property…

When that rainy day finally arrives…

They never actually end up using their savings.

Because the truth is, they’re not saving because of anything besides FEAR.

If you want to achieve any success financially, you have to make the mental shift from scarcity to abundance.

You have to start USING money. It’s a tool.
.
